  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He knocked on his table, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] take this, what I told you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That is the truth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Shut up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The third question, the most important one what I remember, and is not to forget it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know that-- and now-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there is a lot of other partisans, like the Russian partisans, the Jewish partisans, and all others, Armia Ludowa, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we are fighting them.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And a lot of partisans are Jews there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We are fighting them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If that would be that you have to shoot them, if you will listen and we will fulfill the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE]--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The command.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was thinking what else I heard this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Commandant, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I know the history of Jews for the all hundreds and hundreds of years, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews are all over the world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A Jew-- a Polish Jew was shooting to a German Jew, and a German Jew, vice versa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A Russian Jew was shooting to a Jewish Jew, and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Unfortunately, that our-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we are in such a situation [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that we would have to fulfill the orders.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But unfortunately, we are in such a situation, the diaspora, the Jews, they are all everywhere, and one is killing the other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there's no other way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Unfortunately, one Jew has to kill the other Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he finished the interrogation, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and he said to us, you are [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] able to talk another few other languages, Russian, Polish.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
